# CategoryAPI

This is a list of _every_ public symbol in SDL, in alphabetic order. You
probably want to look at the [API by category](APIByCategory) instead.

- [Categories](#categories)
- [Functions](#functions)
- [Datatypes](#datatypes)
- [Structs](#structs)
- [Enums](#enums)
- [Macros](#macros)
